text: The Château de Quintin is a castle in Quintin, Côtes-d'Armor, Brittany, France. ==History== The castle was partly built in 1775.French Ministry of Culture: Château de Quintin ==Architectural significance== It has been listed as an official monument since 1983. ==References== Category:Châteaux in Côtes-d'Armor Category:Monuments historiques of Côtes-d'Armor
title: Château de Quintin
